gov.nasa.jpf.vm

Class GlobalTrackingPolicy

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.nasa.jpf.vm.SharedObjectPolicy
      • gov.nasa.jpf.vm.GlobalTrackingPolicy

  • public class GlobalTrackingPolicy
extends SharedObjectPolicy
    a SharedObjectPolicy that uses search global ThreadInfoSets, i.e. we remember thread access of all previously executed paths. For instances, we use the object reference value to retrieve cached values For static fields, we just use the corresponding class object reference Note that this policy requires search global object ids (SGOID), i.e. only works with Heap implementations providing SGOIDs
